{"tid":2284574,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"宇宙在不斷升溫，科學家測出氣體平均溫度較早期高了 10 倍","createTime":"2020-11-13T11:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T14:52:08.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"087cbed83a097151c08686addb4aed2485a6e55a","tid":2284574,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgur.com/1QZgRNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F1QZgRNU.jpg&h=34d29914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地球正在因人類活動大量排放的溫室氣體升溫中，而我們的宇宙其實也因引力塌縮在漸漸<br />\n變熱。最新研究發現，宇宙如今溫度比 100 億年前還要高約 10 倍，並且隨著時間推移<br />\n會一直加熱下去。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2020/11/12/temperature-cosmic-dark-matter-universe/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2020%2F11%2F12%2Ftemperature-cosmic-dark-matter-universe%2F&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=2e656ae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2020/11/12/temperature-cosmic-dark-matter-universe/</a>"},{"pid":"05c3a9eead5f00fe3091a27112567e7cc9ff7051","tid":2284574,"uid":317498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:42:03.000Z","msg":"宇宙大爆炸"},{"pid":"b1c8f90f99dfbf9e11d36caae9f7345860a2fafa","tid":2284574,"uid":79117,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:42:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31e468f8c9c589b7961b88650cf65bdbc400eb52","tid":2284574,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:51:21.000Z","msg":"點define 宇宙溫度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e9c36676d3569bcef8c4095a906ef73d23ae13","tid":2284574,"uid":79789,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T11:52:51.000Z","msg":"地球暖化撚:地球既二氧化碳已經影響到宇宙"},{"pid":"69574a5dd94be4108008f2f4280911b10fbdd3dd","tid":2284574,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e468f8c9c589b7961b88650cf65bdbc400eb52","ti